summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting electrical overhead and underground distribution easements over portions of Victory Heights; vacated South Hanford Street; Richmond Acres Addition; Plat of Pritchard Island Addition to the City of Seattle; vacated North 165th Street; the northwest quarter of Section 18, Township 23 North, Range 4 East; and Lake Forest Park Estates, as described below and placing said easements under the jurisdiction of the City Light Department.
